{
  "texts": [
    "Fine-tuned mT5 large using LoRA on data from all 12 languages.",
    "We expect this model to perform worse than ours due to the noise from the language mix.",
    "Since our HQL models are trained on 1 487 856 instances (cf.",
    "subsection 6.2), we let this multilingual model train up to that many instances.",
    "Generate and Translate (Gen&Trans)."
  ]
}